{"tid":1152771,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"魔咒或者係報應， 點解猁一直拎唔到首次英超","createTime":"2019-05-13T07:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T11:42:26.000Z","uid":118090,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"997b8e26ddf346134fe2ec7b82b661d8f113f3eb","tid":1152771,"uid":118090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kc6wWt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kc6wWt.png&h=ec39912a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n94 年， 當時猁仲可以話自己係英國拎最高級別聯賽冠軍次數球隊， 係18 次. 記住94 年已拎左18 次頂級聯賽. <br />\n<br />\n當曼94 年拎首個英超那年， 作客Anfield 時， 比猁迷整左張banner, 叫曼聯贏夠18 次冠軍先再黎Anfield.<br />\n<br />\n當然曼其後贏到18 冠軍都實現番承諾， 到番Anfield.<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪呢個就係報應， 由94 年至今， 猁一個英超都未拎到.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GedbZX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GedbZX.png&h=090c99b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4976f6bea1c64c9dcf4dba219277a09917f709cb","tid":1152771,"uid":7435,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"真係唔知邊個撩事鬥非先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89419503aaf601fbfa23a20485838e66f1034c1c","tid":1152771,"uid":223534,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"假利 真利一定好低調唔會串唔會咬人"},{"pid":"f65edb2706233e793297dc53c7fa7ec483f14091","tid":1152771,"uid":11254,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/26993891_839527939583906_376398685462821852_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=d6dd3f6ecca78bc57f83cc8b9bdea0e5&amp;oe=5D726DCB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F26993891_8